  "text": "In order to clarify a little bit, I'd like to ask a question if we have a highly polarized entity polarized towards service to others, and as a highly polarized entity polarized towards service to self. What would be, taking each ray, starting with red, would there be a difference in the the red ray of these two entities? I am Ra. This shall be the last full question of this working. There is no difference in equally strongly polarized positive and negative entities as regards red ray.",
